                <h1>Therapist Office: Creating a Calm and Safe Space</h1>
                <p>A therapist office should evoke a sense of calm and safety. Choose soft, neutral colors for walls that promote relaxation. Incorporate comfortable seating and natural light to create a welcoming atmosphere. Use decor like plants or art that encourages tranquility and reflection. It's vital for clients to feel at ease in this space.</p>
